Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.44,0:00:11.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With his face shimmering brightly in the pitch black darkness...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.53,0:00:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and his eyes like all the stars in the sky gathering as one...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.49,0:00:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...he told me that eternity does exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.79,0:00:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even now, I clearly remember how he was that night, when he was only seventeen years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.98,0:00:52.86,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Usotsuki na anata nakimushi no atashi
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.86,0:00:58.82,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Doushite umaku ikanai wa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.82,0:01:04.96,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Oshare shita kami mo rain suton no tsume mo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.96,0:01:10.92,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Anata wa kidzuki mo shinai ne
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.92,0:01:18.30,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Love kanashii namida nanka ja nai yo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.30,0:01:23.02,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Me ga kawaite hirihiri suru dake
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.02,0:01:28.94,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kono unmei bakari I love
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.86,0:01:37.82,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kimi dake wo atashi dake wo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.82,0:01:42.74,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Atsui omoi wo uketomete
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.95,0:01:49.88,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Doko made mo tsunagattetai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.88,0:01:56.63,Romaji OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kawaikunai nakigao mo se mo aishiteru
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.98,0:00:52.86,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't things go well between
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.86,0:00:58.82,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,the liar, you, and the crybaby, me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.82,0:01:04.96,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't notice my styled hair
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.96,0:01:10.92,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,or my nice set of press-on nails.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.92,0:01:18.30,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Love isn't about the unhappy tears that go along with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.30,0:01:23.02,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Those tears only leave my eyes dry and hurt me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.02,0:01:28.94,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,I love this destiny
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.86,0:01:37.82,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,between only you and only me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.82,0:01:42.74,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to accept your hot feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.95,0:01:49.88,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,and be taken by you forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.88,0:01:56.63,english OP S,,0000,0000,0000,,Despite your uncute, tearful face and your shortness, I still love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.22,0:02:10.73,Episode title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(800,960)\pos(160,381)\fscx112.5\fscy103.75}Episode 20 ...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.06,0:02:10.77,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? The girl from the hook-up party the other day?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.77,0:02:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. As it turns out, I'm seeing her again this weekend.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.73,0:02:16.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But meeting her by myself is a little embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.49,0:02:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You, embarrassed? That's a rare sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.40,0:02:20.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not me! Her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.53,0:02:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She asked if she could come with a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.24,0:02:25.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, would you come, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.45,0:02:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Go see her by yourself! Such a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.08,0:02:30.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please! Pretty please?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.79,0:02:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You only have to stay for half the time! So won't you come, friend of mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.38,0:02:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.88,0:02:38.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only guy I know who's always doing nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.22,0:02:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you at {\fnComic Sans MS\fs35}1 {\fnFertigo Pro\fs33}PM tomorrow at the plaza in front of the station!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.56,0:02:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.02,0:02:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What jacket are you going to wear on Sunday?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.02,0:02:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Why do you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.11,0:02:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're not going to wear one, I was thinking of wearing my stadium jumper.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.57,0:02:58.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, my red one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.49,0:03:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that one? The one that looks a lot like mine, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.82,0:03:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why wouldn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.57,0:03:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we both wore the same one, we'd have that whole couple look going, and that'd be kinda scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.04,0:03:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with the couple look?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.20,0:03:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, don't say that! Don't you dare wear yours, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.50,0:03:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, what should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.83,0:03:13.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.71,0:03:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to keep you waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.71,0:03:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.47,0:03:22.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my friend. He was with us the other day, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.13,0:03:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right! Hi there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.59,0:03:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.55,0:03:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, let's get going!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.64,0:03:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we go get a cup of tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.02,0:03:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really know what hits the spot! Where should we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.48,0:03:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nice having you as a fellow tag-along today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.44,0:03:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, yeah! Same with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.44,0:03:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You see, I can't really handle really spicy food.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.07,0:03:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine! Why don't we have something you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.62,0:03:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go! Open wide!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.33,0:03:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did he really need me to come along...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.92,0:03:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The other day...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.00,0:03:59.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the hook-up party, you sat on the far right the whole time, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.51,0:04:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was on the left, so we never got a chance to speak, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.43,0:04:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... yeah... was it like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.30,0:04:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Are you sure you just don't like hook-up parties?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.31,0:04:11.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.10,0:04:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, do you remember my name?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.69,0:04:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry... I'm really sorry. I'm bad at remembering names.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.24,0:04:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's alright. I never really stand out at those things anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.57,0:04:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true! You're cute, Chisa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.91,0:04:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Chisa-chan, you were the most popular girl there! No joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.92,0:04:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though you're my number one, my cute little Mai!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.79,0:04:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're so honest! Open wide!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.55,0:04:41.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's good...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.76,0:04:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it good?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.34,0:04:44.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.38,0:04:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.14,0:04:50.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though you were the most popular, you're just a tag-along today?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.39,0:04:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... I really think you have to like the person back, or it won't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.35,0:04:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.39,0:04:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You couldn't be more right! I feel the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.61,0:05:04.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takeuchi-kun... don't you have someone you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.45,0:05:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.95,0:05:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... it ended up not working out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.21,0:05:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I got all desperate and ended up going to that hook-up party.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.96,0:05:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be hard getting over that sort of stuff, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.97,0:05:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.64,0:05:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sure was good!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.10,0:05:32.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a good meal!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.18,0:05:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where should we go next?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.69,0:05:39.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wherever you want Mai-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.19,0:05:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A perfect escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.94,0:05:45.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those two should be fine by themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.61,0:05:48.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to believe she thought it would be embarrassing by herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.24,0:05:50.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's leave them alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.79,0:05:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.12,0:05:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good work today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.79,0:05:59.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The bus I take is this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.13,0:06:05.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, umm... have a safe trip home, Miyata-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.76,0:06:10.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.76,0:06:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was all a lie! I had those two set this whole thing up for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.39,0:06:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just really wanted to see you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.64,0:06:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since I didn't have a chance to talk to you the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.57,0:06:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And when I actually had the chance today, you turned out to be the type of person I thought you were...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.91,0:06:33.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A really, really nice person.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.45,0:06:39.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for lying and fooling you like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.42,0:06:44.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you don't like these sorts of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.05,0:06:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But would you please consider hanging out with me some more?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.59,0:06:54.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you please give me a chance and go out with me for just one month?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.19,0:07:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so heavy...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.53,0:07:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lala... don't jump on me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.70,0:07:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lalami. Lala.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.17,0:07:26.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nana... Nanami. You're heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.05,0:07:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get on top of me like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.96,0:07:30.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.47,0:07:35.60,test,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord1\shad1\c&H847AFF&\3c&H85D9FF&\an8\4c&H85D9FF&\b1\pos(320,1)\fscx175\fscy190}Sign: A refreshing Sunday morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.31,0:07:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is this, first thing in the morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.52,0:07:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be borrowing your room today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.94,0:07:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time to celebrate...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.15,0:07:44.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Take-chan's first girlfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.61,0:07:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, the girl asked him to give her a chance, and to go out with her for a month!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.36,0:07:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, you just can't turn down those sorts of things!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.03,0:07:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, here he comes! Hurry and prepare the party poppers!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.12,0:07:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.74,0:08:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But don't you think the whole time limit thing is awesome?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.04,0:08:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, you never really know until you go out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.75,0:08:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Congrats!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.30,0:08:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... have plans for today, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.22,0:08:20.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dumbass.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.18,0:08:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nana-chan, I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.60,0:08:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nana-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.44,0:08:30.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It totally skipped my mind. I didn't do it on purpose. I swear.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.36,0:08:26.90,test,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord1\shad1\3c&H85D9FF&\an8\4c&H85D9FF&\frz283.465\fscx235\fscy210\pos(311,260)\c&H6297EE&}Red jacket
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.40,0:08:27.86,test,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord1\shad1\3c&H85D9FF&\an8\4c&H85D9FF&\frz283.465\fscx235\fscy210\pos(311,260)\c&H6297EE&}Red jacket
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.40,0:08:28.90,test,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord1\shad1\3c&H85D9FF&\an8\4c&H85D9FF&\frz283.465\fscx235\fscy210\pos(311,260)\c&H6297EE&}Red jacket
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.36,0:08:29.90,test,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord1\shad1\3c&H85D9FF&\an8\4c&H85D9FF&\frz283.465\fscx235\fscy210\pos(311,260)\c&H6297EE&}Red jacket
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.28,0:08:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After I went on and on about it the day before last.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.74,0:08:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.61,0:08:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't listen to anything I say.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.24,0:08:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.33,0:08:40.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before I left, things were a little crazy...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.41,0:08:42.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What else could you have possibly been thinking about when you put it on?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.17,0:08:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.25,0:08:51.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take you somewhere nice. So, forgive me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.80,0:08:58.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be tricked so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.05,0:08:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We shall see, won't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.60,0:09:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, put on your jacket.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.22,0:09:05.02,note,,0000,0000,0000,,Sign: Pet Land
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.06,0:09:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're so adorable! I could just eat them all up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.82,0:09:10.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Lalami is the best, though!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.65,0:09:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, it's a corgi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.57,0:09:14.57,test,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fscx295\fscy296.25\c&H667481&\b1\frx344\fry32\pos(465,95)\frz24.192}Parakeets
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.66,0:09:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are squirrels over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.45,0:09:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a sec! I'm gonna make this my background.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.58,0:09:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was so much fun, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.75,0:09:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look refreshed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.96,0:09:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could definitely own a corgi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.00,0:09:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The kittens were so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.67,0:09:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But my Lalami's the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.92,0:09:39.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... do you think you can fall in love with someone you don't like to begin with?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.89,0:09:42.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this, so out of the blue?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.43,0:09:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For example, even if you don't like someone, you still go out with them and force yourself to fall for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.02,0:09:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like someone now I used to hate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.19,0:09:55.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.15,0:09:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.28,0:10:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? You hated me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.33,0:10:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When we were freshmen, yeah. Why are you so shocked?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.83,0:10:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't he realize...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.37,0:10:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't they say love and hate are two sides of the same coin?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.79,0:10:12.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You get mad because they're "stuck in your head", right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.01,0:10:16.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you say something like that before?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.05,0:10:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But some things never go right with these things, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.68,0:10:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What doesn't?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.01,0:10:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.85,0:10:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How so?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.52,0:10:28.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For example...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.81,0:10:31.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A couple in red!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.52,0:10:33.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's really popular, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.61,0:10:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yano, let's not holds hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.44,0:10:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine! Just forget that ugly woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.53,0:10:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You moron! Doofus!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.53,0:10:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For example, when your boyfriend's being a complete moron and you want to kick him...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.08,0:10:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...his smile ends up being too cute, and you forgive him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.00,0:10:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You always give in to your feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.76,0:11:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Love is the opposite of great effort, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.52,0:11:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell that to him, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.53,0:11:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.62,0:11:27.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you, Nana-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.76,0:11:43.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will love come to Ms. Mizuguchi Kana?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.18,0:11:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How will the last episode turn out?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.89,0:11:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will she fall in wonderful love, or will someone fall in wonderful love with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.02,0:11:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Come to me, love! Come love, come!"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.10,0:11:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mizuguchi Kana will now sing "Come On, My Love"!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.53,0:11:59.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on my love!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.24,0:12:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I've been saying, it has to be love when girls take off their glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.78,0:12:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so obvious now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.12,0:12:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But who'd go out with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.70,0:12:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.71,0:12:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't even have a girlfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.29,0:12:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're evil to suggest someone like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.83,0:12:16.63,overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you are single!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.44,0:12:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They don't suit you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.81,0:12:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just not used to them yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.19,0:12:40.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dirt gets in them so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.11,0:12:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your eyes are bright red, like a rabbit's.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.18,0:13:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look better in glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.47,0:13:10.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Rabbit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.36,0:13:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna go get another ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.37,0:13:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Moto.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.80,0:13:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you getting so mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.76,0:13:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.85,0:13:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are things you just can't know until you try going out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.27,0:13:58.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just try going out with her for a month.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.60,0:14:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Well, it looks like I really couldn't fall for you. Sorry!"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.70,0:14:08.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would've been much better to decline at the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.32,0:14:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.83,0:14:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saying you'll "try going out for a month" is the same as saying you'll keep going out after a month!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.29,0:14:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.08,0:14:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been prepared for that much since the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.29,0:14:22.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate me, moron.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.75,0:14:26.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? So you'll go out with her even though you don't like her?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.13,0:14:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure like to volunteer for anything, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.68,0:14:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going out with her to fall for her!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.39,0:14:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.64,0:14:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sound so sure of yourself, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.43,0:14:38.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, you've never fallen for someone who's fallen for you first.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.31,0:14:40.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It might happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.56,0:14:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think so. I'd go so far as to swear it won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.77,0:14:44.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what do you suggest?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.78,0:14:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go out with some girl you don't even like. You're just wasting time!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.37,0:14:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to hear that coming from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.37,0:15:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just think about making your own girl not cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.42,0:15:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.59,0:15:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.63,0:15:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.47,0:15:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You little...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.93,0:15:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh... What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.47,0:15:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,J-Just some advice on how to style his hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.19,0:15:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the hottest and coolest look this fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.36,0:15:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think it'd look cool to lengthen your sideburns some more?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.73,0:15:28.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just take some from the left.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.24,0:15:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I was just thinking the same thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.70,0:15:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all about the lack of balance, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.49,0:15:35.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... isn't that Yano's hair in your hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.91,0:15:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're already losing this much hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.04,0:15:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, I'll give it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.21,0:15:43.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This could be bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.46,0:15:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blood... Takeuchi-kun, you're bleeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.96,0:15:48.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say if you lick it, it'll heal!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.09,0:15:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lick, lick, lick!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.09,0:15:49.59,overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.89,0:15:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you two weren't fighting?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.85,0:15:57.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Us? Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.06,0:16:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moto, I went too far. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.32,0:16:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine. After all, I'm usually the one going too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.78,0:16:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do understand what you're saying. You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.42,0:16:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I... need to move forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.71,0:16:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.89,0:16:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of girl is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.43,0:16:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like Kanno Miho...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.48,0:16:43.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanno?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.43,0:16:43.56,note,,0000,0000,0000,,Note: A famous Japanese actress and J-Pop singer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.81,0:16:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take her, and make her a little more plain.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.86,0:16:49.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No idea what you're talking about...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.78,0:16:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's really pale.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.62,0:16:58.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.70,0:17:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think she's a good girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.38,0:17:10.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi! Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.35,0:17:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I brought your notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.14,0:17:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You could've just brought it to school tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.52,0:17:26.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was no reason to come out this late.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.27,0:17:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.98,0:17:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And here are some steamed meat buns.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.73,0:17:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Steamed meat buns?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.99,0:17:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I heard Takeuchi-kun got a girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.49,0:17:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't you be happy for him?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.25,0:17:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's no good, Yano.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.71,0:17:49.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because it's not like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.46,0:17:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm... I think love that you have to work at is also all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.34,0:17:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with that? You're weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.80,0:18:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not too sure myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.89,0:18:04.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're too split on the issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.52,0:18:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted Take to go out with a girl he actually liked.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.36,0:18:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, he's a really good guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.45,0:18:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.00,0:18:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why everything will be all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.46,0:18:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since the girl he's going out with is a girl who can understand that goodness in him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.79,0:18:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll definitely turn out okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.76,0:18:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.89,0:18:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your hair's wet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.10,0:18:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, maybe. I took a bath earlier tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.02,0:18:54.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll catch a cold like that! Don't tell me those are your PJ's?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.07,0:18:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take my sweater.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.98,0:18:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right! You'll catch a cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.70,0:19:00.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got a lot on underneath, so I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.41,0:19:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then should I warm you up some more?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.91,0:19:04.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be too embarrassing if someone walks by! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.21,0:19:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's... not wearing a bra!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.22,0:19:22.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah. I've got a bandana in my pocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.14,0:19:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.81,0:19:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This way, your head should be protected from the cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.23,0:19:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Little Red Riding Hood!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.45,0:19:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to go on a trip with you, Takahashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.70,0:19:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I know we can't go, not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.79,0:19:54.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're in no hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.17,0:20:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it doesn't have to be a full-blown trip...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.18,0:20:07.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd just like to go somewhere... someplace where we can be alone together.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.89,0:20:13.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someplace where no one can disturb us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.98,0:20:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someplace where we don't have to think about having to go home later...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.36,0:20:20.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...or where we don't have to go our separate ways for the evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.16,0:20:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to hurry and become an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.08,0:20:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to hurry and become an adult... so I can come and steal you away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.31,0:20:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If only... there was such a thing as eternity.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.74,0:21:04.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.99,0:21:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It does exist. I'm sure of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.39,0:21:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With his face shimmering brightly in the pitch black darkness...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.65,0:21:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and his eyes like all the stars in the sky gathering as one...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.66,0:21:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...he told me that eternity does exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.62,0:21:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even now, I clearly remember how he was that night, when he was only seventeen years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.58,0:22:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though we're now both adults, we know there's no such thing as eternity.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.68,0:22:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that we're no longer kids...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.18,0:22:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But back then... time truly stopped, and we were the only people in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.07,0:22:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That moment was so real... and yet so dreamlike...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.66,0:22:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It felt like it only lasted a moment... yet also an eternity.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.91,0:22:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Within our youthful hearts at the time, I'm sure eternity really existed.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.01,0:22:50.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.47,0:22:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, yeah. I saw your message.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.06,0:22:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's no problem. It's really no problem at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.64,0:22:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Then, see you tomorrow in front of the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.82,0:23:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.08,0:23:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.00,0:23:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...eventually becomes an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.17,0:21:22.13,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Ima kimi ga iikaketa kotoba ga
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.13,0:21:28.30,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Yubisaki ni sotto oritekita
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.30,0:21:34.94,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Nanimo iwanakute ii yo
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.94,0:21:40.73,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsumaida yubi wo gyutto atatamete
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.73,0:21:57.25,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kotoba wa kotoba dakara kokoro hanbun mo tsutaenai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.25,0:22:10.43,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Setsunakute modokashikute yuuyake futari wo tsutsundeiru
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.43,0:22:23.19,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Komiageru mune no omoi kokoro ga itai yo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.26,0:22:53.85,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Moshi kimi ga tabibito ni nattara
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.85,0:23:00.56,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kore gurai kimi wo matteru darou
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.56,0:23:06.61,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kisetsu wa kawaru sono tabi ni
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.61,0:23:12.58,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kioku ga usuragu koto ga attemo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.58,0:23:29.09,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,dareka wo konna fuu ni kokoro ippai de aisenai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.09,0:23:36.39,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Mamaritai taisetsu na kimi
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.39,0:23:42.31,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Itsu datte futari wa hitori ja nai
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.31,0:23:49.99,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Kono mune ga kawaresou de
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.99,0:23:56.12,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Furete hoshii yo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.25,0:24:12.05,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Setsunakute modokashikute kaerenai kono mama aruiteitai
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.05,0:24:27.36,Romaji ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Yabaisaki ni kanjiteiru kokoro no kotoba wo
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.17,0:21:22.13,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,The words you were just about to say
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.13,0:21:28.30,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,fell softly onto my fingertips.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.30,0:21:34.94,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.94,0:21:40.73,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll clasp your hand tightly and warm it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.73,0:21:57.25,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Because words are words, I can't express half of the feelings in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.25,0:22:10.43,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so wrenching and irritating as the sunset engulfs the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.43,0:22:23.19,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,My heart aches from all the feelings welling up inside of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.26,0:22:53.85,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,If you were to become a traveler,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.85,0:23:00.56,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,would I be able to wait for you as I do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.56,0:23:06.61,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,As the seasons change,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.61,0:23:12.58,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,even if our memories are to fade.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.58,0:23:29.09,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't be able to love someone with all of my heart like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.09,0:23:36.39,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to protect the precious you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.39,0:23:42.31,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,The two of us are never alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.31,0:23:49.99,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,Me heart feels so fragile
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.99,0:23:56.12,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,and I want you to touch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.25,0:24:12.05,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so wrenching and irritating that I can't go home. I want to keep walking like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.05,0:24:27.36,english ED S,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel the words from your heart on my fingertips.
