Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.77,0:25:10.49,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you sleep\N over on Sunday night?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.49,0:25:14.03,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought we'd be able\N to be together all day, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.03,0:25:15.74,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamamoto's mom collapsed...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.74,0:25:17.74,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,...and I'm with her\N at the hospital right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.74,0:25:19.37,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,Why today, of all days...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.37,0:25:21.95,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,...do you choose\N Yamamoto-san over me...?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.95,0:25:24.75,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.75,0:25:26.25,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.04,0:25:29.75,after ending,,0000,0000,0000,,I've loved you this whole time...
